Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron karar Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaida mai ban tsoro a ranar Alhamis a daya daga cikin tashoshin talabijin shida na Brett Kavanaugh, dan takarar babban kotun Amurka, da kuma Christine Blasey Ford, matar da ta zarge shi da wani abin da ake zargin ya faru a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, rikici na siyasa ya ci gaba, yayin da tashoshin watsa labarai suka katse shirye-shiryen yau da kullum don abin mamaki na ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Jeff Flake, Sanata na Arizona, ya shirya don bincika tuhumar har tsawon mako guda.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa tana da tabbacin cewa wani mutum mai shan giya mai suna Kavanaugh ya taba ta kuma ya yi kokarin cire mata tufafinta a lokacin wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh ya bayyana a cikin shaidar da ya yi cewa ya tabbata da cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ruwaito sun kalli ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya lissafa matsakaicin yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu bayanai ba a nan take game da sauran cibiyoyin da suka watsa zaman, kamar su PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma yakan yi wahalar ƙidaya mutanen da suke kallo a ofis.
Idan aka kwatanta, wannan kamar wasan wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ne ko kuma bikin Oscars.
Tashar Fox News, wadda ke goyon bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ita ce ta fi yawan masu kallo a ranar da aka yi zaman, inda ta samu matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69, a cewar Nielsen.
ABC ta bi ta da kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da masu kallo miliyan 3.1 , NBC tana da masu kallo miliyan 2.94 , MSNBC tana da masu kallo miliyan 2.89 kuma CNN tana da masu kallo miliyan 2.52, a cewar Nielsen.
Bayan taron, jama'a sun ci gaba da nuna sha'awarsu.
Flake shi ne babban mutumin da ya yi sanadin abin da ya faru a ranar Juma'a.
Bayan ofishin 'yan jam'iyyar Republican mai tsaka-tsakin ya fitar da sanarwar cewa zai goyi bayan Kavanaugh da kuri'arsa, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun yi rikodin masu zanga-zanga suna ihu a kansa a safiyar Juma'a yayin da yake kokarin hawa kan lif zuwa wani zaman kotun shari'a.
Ya tsaya na 'yan mintoci yana kallon sa yana kallon sa ana zaginsa a CNN.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", in ji wata mata.
Kana ganin yana gaya wa jama'a gaskiya?
Wani ya yi ihu: "Kana da iko, amma mata da yawa ba su da iko".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya fitar da sanarwa, kuma kafin a rufe lif, ya kara da cewa zai ce da yawa a lokacin sauraron karar.
Dukan tashoshin sun watsa labaran ne kai tsaye, sa'ad da aka kai ga zaben da aka yi na majalisar dokoki bayan sa'o'i kadan, game da nadin Kavanaugh a majalisar dattawa.
Amma Flake ya ce zai amince da shi ne kawai idan har FBI ta bincika zargin da ake yi wa wanda aka zaba a mako mai zuwa, abin da 'yan Democrat ke ta nacewa.
Wani abu da ya rinjayi Flake shi ne abokinsa Chris Coons, dan majalisar dattawa kuma dan Democrat.
Flake ya yanke shawarar bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu sanatoci.
Zaɓin Flake yana da muhimmanci, domin ya bayyana cewa 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'un da suka dace ba don amincewa da Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya bude wani bincike na FBI kan zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh.
