An kashe daruruwan mutane a girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka afka a Indonesia, kuma adadin yana ƙaruwa
Wata babbar girgizar kasa da tsunami a tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia ta kashe mutane 384 kuma ta kwashe mutane da yawa daga cikin yankin yayin da manyan raƙuman ruwa suka yi ta faduwa a bakin teku, in ji hukumomi a ranar Asabar.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru a ranar Juma'a domin bikin a bakin teku a birnin Palu, lokacin da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayin mita shida suka yi karo da gaɓar teku a lokacin da gari ya fara duhu, inda mutane da yawa suka rushe, kuma raƙuman ruwan suka lalata duk abin da suka samu.
An yi wannan girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 a kan sikelin Richter.
"A lokacin da barazanar tsunami ta taso a jiya, mutane sun kasance a bakin rairayin bakin teku, ba su bar wurin ba, kuma sun zama wadanda suka kamu da tsunami", in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar agajin bala'i ta BNPB a Jakarta.
"Tsunami ya kawo wasu haɗari: ya jawo motoci, bishiyoyi, gidaje, ya buge komai a ƙasa", in ji Nugroho, wanda ya kara da cewa tsunami ya yi tafiya a cikin teku mai gudu da ke kaiwa kilomita 800 a awa daya kafin ya kai gabar teku.
Ya ce wasu mutane sun hau itace don su tsere wa tsunami kuma sun tsira.
An kwashe mutane 16,700 zuwa cibiyoyi 24 a Palu.
Hotunan sama da hukumar agaji ta bayar sun nuna cewa gine-gine da kantuna da dama sun lalace, gadaje sun karye kuma sun rushe, kuma ruwa ya rufe wani masallaci.
A ranar Asabar, annobar ta ci gaba da girgiza birnin da ke bakin teku.
An ji girgizar ƙasa a yankin da ke da mutane miliyan biyu da dubu huɗu.
Hukumar tantancewa da amfani da fasaha ta Indonesia (BPPT) ta ce a cikin wata sanarwa cewa karfin da aka saki a girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da aka yi a ranar Juma'a ya ninka na bam din nukiliya da aka jefa a Hiroshima a yakin duniya na biyu sau 200.
Ya ce yana yiwuwa yanayin birnin, wanda ke a ƙarshen wani dogon bakin teku, ya ƙara girman tsunami.
Nugroho ya bayyana lalacewar a matsayin "mai yawa" kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, cibiyoyin kasuwanci da otal-otal sun rushe.
Ya ce wasu mutane sun mutu a cikin rugujewar gine-gine, wasu 540 sun ji rauni, 29 kuma sun rasa rayukansu.
Nugroho ya ce adadin wadanda suka mutu da kuma lalacewar da aka yi zai iya kara yawa a gabar tekun mai nisan kilomita 300 a arewacin Palu, a wani yanki da ake kira Donggala, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar.
"Ba mu da wani bayani a kan wannan batu", in ji Nugroho.
"Mutanen da ke zaune a yankin sun fi 300,000", in ji Red Cross a cikin wata sanarwa. "Ma'aikatan Red Cross da masu sa kai suna kan hanyarsu zuwa yankunan da abin ya shafa".
"Wannan bala'i ne, amma zai iya zama mafi muni", in ji Red Cross.
An soki kungiyar ne a ranar Asabar saboda rashin bayyana cewa tsunami ya afkawa Palu, duk da cewa jami'an sun ce raƙuman ruwan sun isa ƙasar a lokacin da aka ba da gargadin.
Hotunan da aka wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna wani mutum yana tsaye a kan wani gini yana ihu yana gargadi mutane cewa tsunami na gabatowa.
Bayan 'yan mintoci kaɗan, ruwa ya faɗo a bakin tekun, ya kwashe gine-gine da motoci.
