Dole ne Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take baiwa AI
Yayin da kasar Sin ke kara shiga harkar kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka yawan kudaden da take kashewa a kan binciken AI, in ji mai zuba jari kuma masanin AI Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Ya faɗi haka ne game da sanarwar da aka yi game da AI daga sassan gwamnati na Amurka, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabara ta AI.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta sanar da shirinta na shekara ta bara, cewa tana son ta zama kasa ta farko a fannin kirkirar kere kere ta hanyar fasaha a shekarar 2030.
"Abin da zai zama kyakkyawan farawa shi ne ninka kasafin kudin bincike kan AI, ganin cewa duk sauran kasashe suna baya da Amurka, kuma muna neman ci gaba a AI", in ji Lee.
Haɗa kuɗin zai iya sa a yi saurin samun nasarar samun babban ci gaba a fannin I.A. a Amirka, in ji Lee a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order aka buga shi a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a Face++, daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI na kasar Sin.
A shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin AI wanda ya doke mafi kyawun dan wasan American Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama manajan Microsoft Research da kuma Shugaban sashin China na Google.
Lee ya nuna godiyarsa ga gasa ta fasaha da gwamnatin Amurka ke gudanarwa, kamar su Robotics Challenge na Hukumar Ci Gaban Bincike ta Tsaro, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a yi gasar ta gaba, saboda zai taimaka wajen gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
A Amirka, Lee ya ce masu bincike sukan yi aiki tuƙuru don samun tallafin gwamnati.
"China ba ta karbar manyan malamanmu ba, kamfanoni ne ke yi", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da manyan jami'o'i a cikin 'yan shekarun nan don su yi aiki a kan AI.
Lee ya ce kokarin da Amurka ke yi na A.I. zai amfana daga sauya tsarin dokokin shige da fice.
"Duk wanda ya sami digirin digirgir a fannin AI, ya kamata a ba shi katin kore ta atomatik", in ji shi.
Majalisar kasa ta kasar Sin ta fitar da shirin bunkasa AI na gaba a watan Yuli na shekarar 2017.
Cibiyar Kimiyya ta kasar Sin tana ba da tallafin kudi ga ma'aikatan jami'o'i, kamar yadda National Science Foundation da sauran hukumomin gwamnati ke ba da kudi ga masu binciken Amurka, amma ingancin aikin kimiyya ya yi kasa a kasar Sin, in ji Lee.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa wani Cibiyar Haɗin Kai na Ilimin Artificial Intelligence, da nufin haɗa abokan hulɗa daga masana'antu da kuma ilimi a cikin wannan yunƙurin, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Zaɓaɓɓen Ilimin Artificial Intelligence.
Kuma a wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar cewa za ta zuba dala biliyan biyu a shirin AI Next.
NSF tana zuba jari sama da dala miliyan 100 a binciken AI.
Amma dokar Amurka da za ta haifar da kafa kwamitin tsaro na kasa don yin amfani da hankali na wucin gadi ta kasance cikin watanni.
