Girka tana da lardi da ake kira Macedonia, kuma tana cewa sunan makwabciyarta ta arewa yana nufin tana da'awar yankin Girka, saboda haka Girka ta kafa dokar hana Macedonia shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Gwamnatocin biyu sun kulla yarjejeniya a watan Yuni bisa sabon sunan da aka gabatar, amma masu kishin kasa sun ce sauya sunan zai lalata asalin kabilar Slavic da ke Macedonia.
