Lokacin taron zaben Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
A wannan daren, Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara wani babban taro na neman zabe a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wuraren da yake so, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da aka dage zaben wanda zai zabi a matsayin babban alkalin kotun, Trump na son ya samu goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a lokacin da jam'iyyar Republican za ta rasa iko a majalisa a lokacin zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai fara a yammacin Virginia kuma yaya kuke kallon wannan a kan layi?
Taron Trump a birnin Wheeling, na jihar West Virginia, zai fara ne a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018, da karfe 7:00 na yamma.
Za ku iya kallon gangamin Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana ne game da sauraron da aka yi wa babban alkalin shari'a Brett Kavanaugh a wannan makon, wanda ya kara nauyi a yayin da ake zargin Kavanaugh da laifin lalata, kuma majalisar dattawa za ta jira har mako guda kafin ta amince da nadin, yayin da FBI ke binciken lamarin.
Amma babban dalilin wannan jerin tarurruka shi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke neman takara a zaben watan Nuwamba su kara samun karfin gwiwa.
Shugaban yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa Trump ya ce, wadannan tarurruka guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, na nufin karfafawa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da na wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Samun iko da majalisa na da muhimmanci ga shirinsa, don haka shugaban ya yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin da ake fara yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
Taron da za a yi a yammacin nan a filin wasa na Wesbanco a birnin Wheeling na iya jan hankalin magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a iya tattauna shi a kafofin watsa labarai na birnin Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump ya kai ziyara karo na biyu a watan jiya a jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo don ya ba shi karin haske a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
