Almanak: Wanda Ya kirkiro na'urar lissafin Geiger
Kuma yanzu shafi daga littafinmu na "Sunday Morning": 30 ga Satumba, 1882, yau daidai shekaru 136 da suka shige, wanda zai iya ƙidaya... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna rediyo, abin da ya kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Tun daga lokacin, Geiger counter ya zama sananne a kimiyya, kuma ya zama alama a al'adun gargajiya, misali a cikin Bells or Coronado, fim na 1950 tare da masu ba da shawara na farko Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Maza: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers:  Wannan na'urar Geiger ce. Ana amfani da ita wajen gano ma'adanai masu aikin rediyo, kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka wannan belun kunne, za ka ji tasirin da atoms ke yi daga aikin rediyo a cikin ma'adanai.
Evans: "Yana da gaske yana fashewa yanzu!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ya cika shekara 63.
Amma abin da ya yi ya ci gaba da kasancewa da muhimmanci.
Sabon rigakafin cutar kansa zai iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikin mutum ganin ƙwayoyin cuta
Sabuwar rigakafin cutar kansa zai iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ta "ga" kuma ta kashe ƙwayoyin cuta
Rigakafin yana koya wa garkuwar jikin mutum gane ƙwayoyin cuta a lokacin magani
Wannan hanya ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga cikin marasa lafiya don canza su a cikin lab
Za su iya ganin furotin da ke faruwa a yawancin ciwon daji, kuma su sake yin allurar.
Wani allurar rigakafin gwaji na ba da kyakkyawan sakamako ga marasa lafiya da ke da nau'ikan ciwon daji.
Wata mata da aka yi mata maganin rigakafin da ke koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki gane ƙwayoyin cuta, ta ga ciwon daji na ƙwanƙwasawa ya ɓace fiye da watanni 18
Wannan hanyar tana ɗaukan ƙwayoyin cuta daga cikin marasa lafiya, kuma a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje, ana gyara ƙwayoyin don su iya ganin furotin HER2, wanda yake da yawa a cikin nau'in ciwon daji, sannan kuma a sake saka ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon Ciwon daji ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa muna da rigakafin da ke da kyau sosai".
HER2 tana "stimulating" ci gaban wasu nau'o'in ciwon daji, ciki har da ciwon nono, ciwon daji na ovarian, ciwon daji na huhu, da kuma ciwon daji na hanji, in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
