Cutar HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar sabbin cututtuka da kashi 14%
China ta ba da rahoton cewa yawan mutanen China da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya ƙaru da kashi 14 cikin ɗari.
Hukumar kiwon lafiya ta ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a ƙasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun faru ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ba haka yake ba.
A dā, cutar HIV ta yaɗu da sauri a wasu ɓangarorin ƙasar Sin ta wurin jinin da aka yi wa jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suke kamuwa da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar ya kusan kusan sifili, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma idan aka kwatanta da wannan lokacin na bara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i na zama babbar matsala a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An dakatar da luwadi a kasar Sin tun shekara ta 1997, amma an ce ana nuna wa mutanen LGBT wariya.
Saboda ra'ayin da ya dace game da ƙasa, an kimanta cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Sau da yawa ana yaɗuwar cututtuka ta rashin kāriya a lokacin jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikacin ma'aikata ya leaked bayanai na Republican 'yan majalisar dattijai da kuma ya kawo a kan "m karya" da kuma "tsarin dabaru".
'Yar majalisar dokokin Amurka Maxine Waters ta yi adawa da zargin cewa wani daga cikin ma'aikatanta ya sanya bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar dattijai uku na Republican a shafin Wikipedia na 'yan majalisa.
Dan Democrat din na Los Angeles ya yi ikirarin cewa masu yada labarai da shafukan yanar gizo na 'yan adawa ne ke yada zarge-zargen.
Waters ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a shafinsa na Twitter, "Ƙarya, ƙarya da kuma ƙarin munanan ƙarya".
An ce bayanan da aka wallafa sun hada da adireshin sirri da lambar wayar sirri na Sanata Lindsey Graham na Amurka daga South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, dukansu daga Utah.
Bayanan sun fito ne a ranar Alhamis, an wallafa su ne a wani shafin yanar gizo da ba a san ko wane ne ba a Capitol Hill a lokacin da ake sauraron wani taro na kwamitin majalisar dattawa game da zargin da ake yi wa Brett Kavanaugh na cin zarafin wani dan takarar zama babban alkalin kotun koli.
An samu wannan rahoto ne bayan da 'yan majalisar dattijai uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
A cewar shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState, adireshin IP da ke nuna asalin sakonnin ya kasance yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma ya ƙunshi bayanan wani ma'aikacin Waters, in ji Hill.
Waters ya ce, "wannan zargi ba shi da tushe, karya ne kuma karya ce".
Wani ma'aikacina, wanda aka yi wa asirinsa, bayanansa da kuma tsaronsa barazana sakamakon wannan zargi na karya, ba shi da alhakin wannan bayanan da aka fitar.
Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe ba, karya ne kuma karya ce.
Sanarwar Waters ta fuskanci suka a yanar gizo, ciki har da tsohon dan jaridar fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda yana da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Daga wannan za ka iya ganin cewa ba ta da halin zama 'yar majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum a kan abin da bai yi ba, kada ya yi fushi.
Kada ya yi tawaye.
Bai kamata ya yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa mai gabatar da kara ya yi wannan shari'ar ba.
Ya kamata ya kasance da kwanciyar hankali.
Fleischer ya bayyana don kwatanta amsar Waters da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zargi da yawan fushi a zaman kotun na ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican da ke neman maye gurbin Waters a zaben fidda gwani, ya kuma bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Mai ƙarfi, idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi.
