"Za mu tabbatar da cewa masu aikata laifin sun bayyana", in ji ta, "kuma za a hukunta su saboda duk ayyukan da suka yi da ke da lahani da kuma hadari ga ma'aikatanta".
Johnny English ya sake kai hari - ɗan ɗan leƙen asiri tare da Rowan Atkinson
A yanzu, a kowane sabon fim da ke da ma'anar Birtaniya, muna neman ambaton Brexit, kuma wannan ya zama gaskiya a wannan farfadowar fim din Johnny English, fim din da ke nuna ɗan leƙen asiri, wanda ya fara ne da Johnny English a 2003, kuma ya sake farfadowa da Johnny English Reborn a 2011.
Wannan maganar ta kaifin baki game da yadda muke rashin nasara za ta zama sabon fitarwa ga kasarmu?
Johnny English wanda ba shi da kwarewa da idanu masu ban mamaki da kuma fuska mai sassauci ya sami nasarar sarrafa komai har zuwa ɗari, har ma da dawowarsa ta biyu. Daga sunansa za ku iya gane cewa shi mutum ne mai ban dariya wanda aka tsara don masu kallo a fina-finai a ƙasashe inda ake magana da harshe banda Turanci.
Hakika, shi ne ɗan leken asiri wanda, duk da cewa yana da ɗan ƙaramin da'awar cewa yana da kyan gani, yana da ɗan Clouseau, ɗan ɗan Mr Bean, da ɗan ɗan ɗan ɗan mutumin da ya ba da gudummawa ga waƙar wasan kwaikwayo na Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe wasannin Olympics na London na 2012.
Asali ya dogara ne akan matafiyi da kuma mutum mai ban mamaki na duniya wanda Atkinson ya taɓa wasa a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard (wanda kowa ya manta a yanzu) wanda koyaushe yana barin wasu rikice-rikice.
A cikin hotonsa na Johnny English, ya nuna wani abu mai ban sha'awa.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da yadda Johnny English yake zuwa wurin wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da makamai na dā kuma yana daɗaɗa ƙwanƙolinsa a kan kwalkwali.
Atkinson zai iya nuna yadda yake da baiwa a fim din na wasan kwaikwayo, amma abin dariya ya zama mai rauni kuma ya wuce gona da iri, musamman ma a yanzu da jerin fina-finai masu tsanani kamar 007 da Mission Impossible sun hada da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan aiki, kuma suna yin hakan da kyau.
Abin dariya kamar ya fi dacewa ga yara fiye da manya, kuma rashin jin daɗin Johnny English ya zama ba na asali ba ne kuma ya fi mayar da hankali fiye da ba'a ba da rubutun da aka yi na hali na Bean wanda Atkinson ya buga.
Maganar da ake ta yi a yanzu ita ce, Birtaniya na cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin wani babban asirin yanar gizo, wanda ya bayyana sunayen dukkan jami'an sirri na Birtaniya, wanda ya ba da mamaki ga jami'in da ke aiki, wanda kuma ya taka rawar gani a matsayin Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya sa aka samu wani firaminista, wata mace mai son kai da ke da matsala a kan kanta kuma ba a son ta sosai a matsayin 'yar siyasa. Emma Thompson tana yin iyakar kokarinta a wannan hali da ke tunatar da ni game da Teresa May, amma rubutun ba ya ba da kayan aiki da yawa don aiki tare.
Ta ce masu ba ta shawara a kan harkokin tsaro sun ce za ta yi amfani da wani ɗan leƙen asiri da ya yi ritaya, tun da yake an ɓata duk wani ɗan leƙen asiri da ke aiki a ƙasar.
Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny English da kansa, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malamin makaranta a wata babbar cibiya, amma yana koyar da aikin ɓoye a cikin baƙon labari.
An kira English zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa kuma ya sake haɗuwa da tsohon ɗan ƙaramin Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, matarsa kuma ta zama kyaftin din jirgin ruwa, rawar da take da ban tsoro da kuma jin dadi wanda bai kai Vicki Pepperdine ba.
Saboda haka, Batman da Robin daga cikin masifar da ta faru a cikin Sirrin Sirrin Mai Girma sun sake dawowa cikin aiki kuma sun sadu da Olga Kurylenko mai ban sha'awa mai ban sha'awa Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista ya yi rashin alheri da ya fadi a hannun wani mai karfin fasaha mai karfin gaske wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara tafiya mai ban sha'awa: suna yin ado kamar masu hidimar, suna ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa, suna yin hayaniya a cikin jirgin ruwan Volta, kuma English ya haifar da rashin tsari lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da kayan aikin Virtual Reality don sanin abubuwan da ke cikin gidan Volta.
An buɗe dukan littattafai game da wannan, amma ko da yake an yi wannan wasan kwaikwayon da kyau kuma yana da ban tsoro, yana sa a tuna da talabijin na yara.
Ba shi da asali sosai.
Kuma kamar sauran fina-finan Johnny English, ina mamakin ko masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya tunanin wani rawa da zai girmama baiwar Rowan Atkinson ba?
