Sarah Palin ta yi magana game da PTSD na Track Palin a taron zaben Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba.
An kama shi kuma an tuhume shi bayan an kai rahoton tashin hankali na gida a ranar Litinin da daddare.
"Ta hanyar abin da ɗana ya fuskanta, abin da ya fuskanta yanzu da ya dawo, ina jin tausayin sauran iyalai da ke fama da sakamakon PTSD da kuma raunin da wasu sojojinmu suka samu", in ji ta ga jama'ar da suka halarci taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
