Washington D.C. da jihohi 18 sun goyi bayan zanga-zangar adawa da sabon tsarin neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da kuma Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan wata doka da ta nuna adawa da sabuwar dokar Amurka da ta hana bautar da wadanda ake zargi da guduwa daga aikata laifukan yan bindiga ko kuma na cikin gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da Washington D.C. sun gabatar da wata sanarwa a kotun Washington na 'abokin kotu' ranar Juma'a don tallafa wa wani mai neman mafaka da ke kalubalantar wannan manufar, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace da Sessions ba, wanda kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta, a kan dokar tarayya.
Ta ce mijinta "da 'ya'yansa maza masu ta'addanci da suke cikin 'yan kungiyar" sun yi mata fyade amma jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas don wannan.
Lauyoyin jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun kwatanta El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, inda mutane da yawa suka nemi mafaka a Amirka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke da matsaloli masu yawa game da ƙungiyoyi da kuma tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta sauya shawarar da Hukumar da ke Kula da Kararrakin Baƙi ta yanke a shekarar 2014 inda ta ba wa baƙi marasa tushe damar neman mafaka.
Karl Racine, babban lauyan Washington D.C., ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yi la'akari da duk wani bukatar neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da kuma yanayin da ake nema, kuma irin wannan toshewar ya saɓa wa wannan ka'ida", in ji wata sanarwa da 'Abokin Kotun ya bayar.
Lauyoyin sun kara da cewa, dokar hana baƙi shiga Amurka tana cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, saboda waɗannan baƙi za su iya zama sabbin masu kasuwanci kuma su "ba da aikin yi ga kasar".
A watan Yuni, Jeff Sessions, Sakataren Shari'a, ya umurci alƙalai su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ake zalunta a gida da kuma waɗanda ake zalunta a ƙungiyoyi.
"Ana samun mafaka ga waɗanda suka gudu daga ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoron tashin hankali bisa ga launin fata, addini, ƙasa, ko kuma kasancewa cikin wani takamaiman rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a cikin sanarwar da ya yi a ranar 11 ga Yuni na manufofin.
Ba a taɓa nufin mafaka ta sauƙaƙa dukan matsaloli ba, ko da yake waɗannan matsaloli suna da tsanani, waɗanda mutane suke fuskanta kowace rana, ko'ina a duniya.
