Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin sabon intanet don ya kai wa Google da Facebook hari
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa wani kamfanin da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Inrupt, sabon aikin da ya fito daga kamfanin, kamfani ne da ke kan hanyar bude tushen dandalin Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanne mutane ke da damar zuwa wane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi barkwanci cewa "mulkin duniya" shi ne ainihin manufar Inrupt.
"Dole ne mu yi wannan yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu 'keɓaɓɓen ajiyar bayanan kan layi' ko POD.
Za a iya ajiye jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar aiki, laburaren waƙa, da wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna tare a cikin burauzar yanar gizo ɗaya, duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ya sa POD ta kasance ta musamman shi ne cewa yana da cikakken dogara ga mai amfani wanda ke da damar shiga abin da bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar da ke bayan Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, aiyuka da kuma kwarewar da ake bukata domin samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin yanzu ya kunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandalin tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu ci gaba da aka yi wa kwangila su yi aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'umma na masu shirye-shirye masu sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere kere a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba za su tattauna da "Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su gabatar da cikakken sauyi wanda zai sa duk tsarin kasuwancin su ya juya gaba daya".
"Ba ma neman izininsu".
A wani rubutu a kan Medium da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "umurnin (Inrupt) shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da zai taimaka wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabon yanar gizo, wanda ake gina a kan Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka-tsakin intanet.
Har ila yau, bayan ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa a matsayin wanda ya kafa kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
