Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji 'ƙasa' saboda halayensa na jima'i
Tom Daley, ɗan wasan tsalle-tsalle na Olympics ya ce ya ji cewa yana ƙasa da wasu domin yadda yake ji game da jima'i sa'ad da yake yaro, amma hakan ya sa ya so ya yi nasara.
Yaron mai shekara ashirin da huɗu ya ce har ya shiga makarantar sakandare, bai fahimci cewa "ba kowa ba ne kamar ni".
A cikin hira da Desert Island Discs a Radio 4 tare da Lauren Laverne, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin gay don ba wa wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce iyaye sun sa ya kasa daraja cin gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, mai gabatar da shirin na tsawon lokaci ya dauki hutun watanni biyu saboda rashin lafiya.
Da alama a matsayin mai jujjuyawar shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce a lokacin ƙuruciyarsa ya ji 'ƙasa' fiye da wasu saboda 'ba a yarda da shi ba don son duka 'yan mata da maza'.
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, waɗannan jiye-jiye, jin kasa da kuma jin bambanci, gaskiya ne da suka ba ni ƙarfin yin nasara".
Yana son ya nuna cewa shi "wani ne" don kada ya sa mutane su yi sanyin gwiwa idan suka gano halinsa.
Wanda ya lashe lambar tagulla biyu a gasar Olympics ya zama babban mai fafutukar gay da kuma bisexual, kuma ya yi amfani da halartarsa a wasannin Commonwealth da aka yi a Australia a wannan shekara don yin kira ga kasashe da dama da su sake yin la'akari da jima'i tsakanin mutane.
Ya ce ya yi magana ne domin yana ganin yana da farin ciki cewa zai iya rayuwa a fili ba tare da ƙarin sakamako ba kuma yana son ya ba wasu 'bege.'
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce, "ya ba ni mamaki sosai" da ya fara son wani mutum, mai shirya fina-finai na Amurka, Dustin Lance Back, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013.
Daley ta auri wanda ya lashe Oscar a shekarar da ta gabata, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, amma ta ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan ka sha wahala sosai tun kana ƙarami", ya shiga gasar Olympics ta farko yana ɗan shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka, yana da wuya ka sami wani a cikin shekarunka da ya sha irin wannan tashin hankali da rashin lafiya.
A watan Yuni ne ma'auratan suka haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "dukkanin ra'ayinsa" ya canja.
"Da a ce kun yi mini wannan tambayar a bara, da na ce duk abin game da lashe lambar zinare ne", in ji shi.
"Amma ka san wani abu, akwai abubuwa da suka fi muhimmanci a duniya fiye da lashe lambar zinare ta Olympics.
"Robin ne lambar zinare ta gasar Olympics".
Sunan ɗansa ya yi daidai da na mahaifinsa wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekara 40, bayan an gano shi da ciwon kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa zai mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambaya shi ne ko sun riga sun samu tikitin zuwa London 2012, domin yana son zama a jere na farko.
"Ban iya samun shi a kan zuciyata in ce, ba za ka zama a gaban layi ba, baba", in ji shi.
"Na riƙe hannunsa sa'ad da ya daina numfashi, kuma ba sai numfashinsa ya daina ba, kuma ya mutu, na fahimci cewa ba shi da iko", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya shiga gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san wannan shine abin da na yi mafarki a rayuwata, yin ruwa a gaban jama'a a wasannin Olympics, babu wani abin da ya fi wannan jin daɗi", in ji shi.
Shi ne kuma ya ba da waƙar da ya fara waƙa, Proud by Heather Small, wanda ya kama shi sosai a hanyar zuwa wasannin kuma har yanzu yana ba shi haushi.
Za a iya sauraron shirin Desert Island Discs a BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 na BST.
Mickelson, ba shi da lafiya, a kan benci a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi yayin da yake buga gasar Ryder Cup ta 47 amma dole ne ya sake samun siffar sa domin kada ya zama abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda ya shiga gasar karo na 12 a shekara biyu, rikodin, kyaftin din tawagar Jim Furyk ya sanya shi a benci don wasan kwallon kafa da na hudu a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar taron, kamar yadda ya saba yi a kan Amurka, wanda ya ci gasar manyan wasanni biyar ya raba ranar tsakanin tallafa wa abokan wasansa da kuma yin atisaye a filin tuki, yana ƙoƙarin gano abin da ya ɓace.
Tun da yake ba a san shi da yin tsalle-tsalle ba ko da a lokacin da yake kan gaba a aikinsa, ɗan shekara 48 ba shi da kyakkyawan zaɓi a kan ƙanƙantar fairways na Le Golf National, inda tsayin ciyawa na roughs ke azabtar da ƙwallon da ke yawo.
Kuma idan filin wasa ba shi da ban tsoro, Mickelson zai yi wasa a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi da Francesco Molinari, wanda ya ci gasar British Open, wanda ke da alaƙa da sabon shiga Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni huɗu a wannan makon.
Idan 'yan Amurkan da suka yi kasa da maki hudu a farkon wasannin guda 12 suka fara wasa da kyau, to wasan Mickelson zai iya zama muhimmiyar wasa.
Furyk ya nuna yana da tabbaci a cikin wannan mutumin, ko da yake gaskiya zai iya wuya a ce ba haka ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci aikin da yake da shi a yau, ya yi mini bulala a baya, ya rungume ni, ya ce zai kasance a shirye gobe".
"Yana da tabbaci sosai.
An saka shi a cikin zauren suna kuma ya ba da gudummawa sosai ga waɗannan ƙungiyoyi, a baya, da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban yi tsammanin zai buga wasanni biyu kawai ba.
Na yi tsammanin zai zama mafi girma, amma shi ne yadda yake kuma shi ne yadda muke ganin ya kamata mu yi.
Yana son ya kasance a wurin kamar yadda kowa yake".
Mickelson zai iya doke Nick Faldo a ranar Lahadi a matsayin dan wasan da ya fi kowacce wasa a gasar Ryder Cup.
Zai iya zama ƙarshen gasar Ryder Cup inda bai taɓa daidaita abubuwan da ya fi so ba.
Mickelson ya ci wasanni 18, ya rasa wasanni 20, kuma ya yi wasa bakwai a kan sa, amma Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa yana da tasiri a kan tawagar.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da ba'a, yana da hankali, yana son yin wa'azin mutane kuma babban mutum ne a cikin tawagar", in ji shi.
"Ina tsammanin 'yan wasan matasa sun ji daɗin yin wasa da shi a wasu lokutan a makon da ya gabata, abin dariya ne a gani.
Yana da fiye da wasa kawai".
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin na tawagar Turai, ya san cewa babban ci gaba zai iya ɓacewa da sauri
Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin na tawagar Turai, ya san daga kwarewa cewa saurin da aka samu kafin wasan guda a ranar ƙarshe ta gasar Ryder Cup, yana iya sauƙaƙe zuwa yanayin da ba shi da dadi.
Dan Dan ya fara wasa a wasan da aka yi a Valderrama a 1997, inda tawagar da ke da kyaftin Seve Ballesteros ta yi nasara da maki biyar a kan Amurkawa, amma a ƙarshe ta wuce layin ƙarshe da mafi ƙarancin bambanci: 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Kuna tuna wa kanku cewa muna da babban nasara a Valderrama; muna da babban nasara a Brookline, inda muka yi asara, kuma a Valderrama, inda muka ci nasara, amma kawai", in ji Bjorn, wanda aka kira a nan, bayan ya ga nasarar da aka samu a 2018 ta 5-3 a ranar Juma'a da kuma jiya, wanda ya kai 10-6 a Le Golf National.
Saboda haka tarihi ya nuna mini da kuma sauran 'yan wasan cewa wannan wasa ba a yi ba tukuna.
Kowa zai yi aiki tukuru a gobe.
Ku ci gaba da shirinku, ku yi shi yadda ya kamata.
Ba a gama ba har sai an rubuta maki a kan allon.
Muna da manufa guda, kuma ita ce, mu ci wannan kofin, kuma dole ne mu ci gaba da mai da hankali a kan hakan.
Ina ci gaba da cewa, ina mai da hankali ne a kan 'yan wasa 12 da muke da su, amma kuma muna sane da mutanen da ke gefen, wasu daga cikin 'yan wasa mafi kyau a duniya".
Da yake farin ciki game da yadda 'yan wasansa suke wasa a kan filin wasan golf, Bjorn ya daɗa: "Ba zan taɓa yin nasara a wannan fagen ba.
Za mu sake fuskantar wata matsala gobe.
Za a tattauna batun mutum-mutumin da ya yi nasara a wasannin da za a yi gobe, kuma wannan wani abu ne da ya bambanta da sauran wasanni.
Yana da kyau a fita waje tare da abokin aiki idan yana da kyau, amma idan kana da kanka, ƙwarewarka a matsayin golfer za ta gwada.
Wannan shi ne sakon da ya kamata ka gaya wa 'yan wasan, ka yi ƙoƙari ka yi mafi kyau gobe.
Saboda haka, bari abokin aikinka ya tafi, kuma ya yi abin da ya dace".
Ba kamar Bjorn ba, abokin hamayyarsa Jim Furyk ya yi tsammanin 'yan wasan sa za su yi fice a matsayin su na abokan wasa, ban da Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, wadanda suka ci maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Furyk da kansa ya samu kwarewa a bangarorin biyu na irin wannan juyin juya halin a ranar karshe, a matsayin memba na tawagar da ta yi nasara a Brookline da kuma a matsayin mai hasara lokacin da Turai ta yi "Mu'ujiza ta Madinah".
"Na tuna da kowane irin magana da aka yi a wannan jawabin", in ji shi, a lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda Ben Crenshaw, kyaftin din kungiyar a 1999, ya yi wa 'yan wasansa kwallo a ranar karshe.
"Muna da wasanni masu muhimmanci 12 da za mu yi gobe, amma bari mu yi kokarin fara wasa da kyau, kamar yadda muke yi a Brooklyn, ko kuma kamar yadda muke yi a Madinah.
Idan muka samu ƙarfin, za mu sami matsi mai yawa a wasan da ke tsakiyar.
Mun tsara jerinmu bisa ga wannan kuma mun tura maza zuwa inda muka ga ya fi kyau, kuma, ka sani, za mu yi kokarin fitar da wani abu daga cikin manyan hat gobe. "
Thomas ya yi kokarin jagorantar adawar, kuma ya sanya Rory McIlroy a wasan farko, kuma Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood da Ian Poulter su ne sauran Turawa a farkon rabin wasan.
"Na zaɓi wannan rukuni a cikin wannan tsari, domin ina tsammanin muna da abin rufewa a kai a kai" in ji Bjorn game da zaɓin 'yan wasan sa na ɗaya.
An Sake Sanya Sabon Jirgin Yaƙin Jamus
Ya kamata sabon jirgin ruwan na Jamus ya fara aiki a shekarar 2014, don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma zai dauki akalla shekara guda kafin a kammala shi, saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma hauhawar farashi, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
An dage fara aiki da 'Rheinland-Pfalz', babban jirgin ruwan sabon nau'in Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit da ke ta da wata mai magana da yawun soji.
Ya kamata jirgin ya shiga cikin rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da ke damun bayan isar da shi sun gurgunta wannan aikin mai girma.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da rundunar ta yi odar su a shekarar 2007 za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwan na Bremen.
Kamar yadda muka sani, suna da babban bindiga, da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoye, kamar rage radar, infrared da kuma sauti.
Sauran muhimman halaye sune tsawon lokacin kulawa, ya kamata ya yiwu a tura sabbin jirage har zuwa shekaru biyu a jere, nesa da tashar jiragen ruwa.
Amma jinkiri na ci gaba yana nufin cewa jiragen yaƙi na zamani, waɗanda aka yi niyya su ba Jamus damar nuna ikonta a ƙasashen waje, sun riga sun tsufa a lokacin da aka fara aiki, in ji Die Zeit.
Frigat F125 da ta yi hatsari ta yi ta samun kanun labarai a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ƙi ta ba da izinin fara aiki da jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi tashar jiragen ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da Sojojin Ruwa suka mayar da jirgin ruwa zuwa wani kamfanin kera jiragen ruwa bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san abin da ya sa aka mayar da jirgin ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu muhimman 'rashin ingantattun kayan aiki da na software' da za su sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka tura shi yaƙi.
Rashin ingancin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci musamman saboda jiragen Baden-Wuerttemberg suna aiki da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na kimanin 120, rabin ma'aikatan jirgin na tsohuwar Bremen.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana fama da matsanancin nauyi, wanda zai rage aikinsa kuma zai rage damar da rundunar ta ke da ita na yin ƙarin gyare-gyare.
Rhineland-Palatinate tana da nauyin tan 7,000, wato, sau biyu na irin jiragen da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da matsalar kayan aiki, farashin duk aikin, har da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin, zai zama matsala.
An ce wannan ya kai € biliyan 3.1 daga € biliyan 2.2 na farko.
Matsalar da sabbin jiragen ruwa ke fuskanta ta zama mai mahimmanci saboda gargaɗin kwanan nan cewa ƙarfin sojojin ruwa na Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokoki a Jamus, ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa suna da "raunin jiragen ruwa da za su iya aiki".
Jami'in ya ce matsalar ta girma kamar ƙwallon kankara a tsawon lokaci, saboda an cire tsoffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a kawo masu maye gurbin ba.
Ya yi gunaguni cewa babu ɗayan jirage masu fashewa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da za a iya ɗaukar su cikin rundunar sojan ruwa.
Ƙungiyar Kula da Ayyukan Ƙasa ta Ƙasa ta Saurari Rayuwar 'Yan Farin Ciki
Wani sabon bincike da aka yi a wani gona a ƙasar Scotland yana ƙoƙarin bayyana yadda namomin kaza suke amfani da shimfidar wuri don neman abinci.
Ana sa rai cewa binciken zai ba da ƙarin haske game da halayen waɗannan dabbobi masu rarrafe masu rarrafe kuma zai taimaka wajen kula da su a nan gaba.
Wani bincike da masana kimiyya na National Trust for Scotland suka yi ya lura da ƙananan ƙanƙara da ƙanƙara, da ƙanƙara mai launin ruwan kasa da kuma ƙanƙara mai ruwa a Inverewe Gardens a Wester Ross.
Ana saka na'urori na musamman na yin fim a wurare masu muhimmanci a kusa da gonar don a lura da ayyukan batirin a duk lokacin da ake shayarwa.
Ma'aikatan NTS da masu sa kai za su yi bincike a kan wayar hannu ta amfani da na'urorin gano abubuwa.
Ƙwararren mai bincike na sauti na dukan hotunan zai ƙayyade yawan kukan da ɗan damisa yake yi da kuma irin abin da yake yi.
Bayan haka, ana yin taswirar wurin da suke da kuma rahoton da zai nuna yadda suke yin abubuwa a ƙasa.
Rob Dewar, mai ba da shawara a kan kiyaye yanayi a hukumar NTS, ya yi fatan cewa sakamakon zai nuna wuraren da mazaunin yake da muhimmanci ga batsa da kuma yadda irin wannan dabbar take amfani da su.
Wannan bayanin zai taimaka wajen tantance fa'idodin kula da mazaunin, kamar samar da wuraren kiwo da kuma yadda za a kula da gandun daji mafi kyau ga batters da sauran nau'o'in.
Yawan batutuwan da ke Scotland da sauran Ingila sun ragu sosai a cikin ƙarni na ƙarshe.
Ana yi musu barazana ta hanyar gine-gine da ayyukan ci gaba da ke shafar wuraren zama da kuma asarar mazauni.
Ƙarfin iska da walƙiya suna iya zama haɗari, kamar yadda masu kama-da-kwarya da wasu abubuwa da ake yi da kayan gini da kuma masu cin naman gida suke.
Amma, a gaskiya, ba makafi ba ne.
Amma, tun da yake suna yin farauta da dare, kunnuwansu sun fi idanunsu amfani wajen kama ganima.
Suna amfani da fasaha mai saurin ganewa da ke nuna inda kwari da kuma wasu abubuwa suke a hanyar da suke bi.
Hukumar NTS, wadda ke kula da gine-gine masu tarihi sama da 270, da manyan lambuna 38, da kuma kadada 76,000 na ƙasar ƙasar, tana ɗaukan batutuwa da muhimmanci.
NTS tana da ƙwararrun masana goma waɗanda suke yin bincike a kai a kai, suna bincika wuraren kwana, kuma a wasu lokatai suna yin ayyukan ceto.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma kafa wurin da ake ajiye batsa na farko da kuma na farko a ƙasar Scotland a gidan Threave a Dumfries da Galloway, inda ake da nau'in batsa takwas cikin goma da ke ƙasar.
Manajan kula da wuraren shakatawa David Thompson ya ce wannan wurin da ake da shi ne wuri mafi kyau da za a iya samun namomin kaza.
Ya ce: "A nan Threave muna da yanayi mai kyau ga batutuwa.
"Muna da tsofaffin gine-gine, da itatuwa da yawa da suka daɗe, da kuma wurin zama mai kyau.
Amma akwai abubuwa da yawa da ba a sani ba game da batsa, kuma saboda haka, aikin da muke yi a nan da kuma wasu wurare zai taimake mu mu fahimci abin da suke bukata don su yi nasara".
Ya jaddada muhimmancin duba batirin kafin gudanar da aikin kula da shi, saboda yiwuwar lalata wurin kwana da gangan zai iya haifar da mutuwar mace 400 da 'ya'yanta, wanda zai iya kawar da dukan mazaunin.
Dabbobin daji dabbobi ne da ake kiyaye su, kuma doka ta hana kashe su, damun su, ko kuma lalata wuraren da suke kwana.
Elisabeth Ferrell, ma'aikaciyar hukumar kula da bat da ke Scotland, ta ce jama'a su ba da gudummawa don taimaka wa.
