2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesiya a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 kuma ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin wadanda ke Aceh.
