An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida, tsangwama a rahoton cin zarafin cikin gida, da kuma yin adawa a lokacin da ake yanke masa hukunci, a cewar wani rahoto da Alaska State Troopers suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce, lokacin da wata mata ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton laifin da ake zarginsa, sai ya kwace wayar daga hannun ta.
