Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman a yanke wa Sajfoello Sajpov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba a wannan jihar tun 1953.
An zargi Sajpov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kori masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke da suka bi hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don a ba da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Sajpov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe da gangan kuma ya yi wa wasu raunuka masu tsanani da gangan, a cewar takardar da aka shigar a kotun kudancin New York da ke neman hukuncin kisa.
Za a iya yanke masa hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu, in ji takardar da aka shigar a kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta amince da tuhumar da ta yi kan tuhuma 22, ciki har da tuhuma takwas na kisan kai domin cin hanci, tuhuma da ake amfani da ita a gaban masu gabatar da kara na tarayya kan aikata laifuka masu tsari, da kuma na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da shiri sosai", a cewar masu gabatar da kara, kuma sun bayyana yadda Sajpov ya kai harin a matsayin "mugu, mai zalunci da lalata".
