An bayyana mafi girman tashin hankali a wannan makon lokacin da aka bayyana sabbin ingantattun, karin haraji kan dala biliyan 200 (150 biliyan euro) na kayayyaki; rabin dukkan kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
