Akwai tabo a wajen kilomita goma daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma a wurare da yawa ba kamar na makon da ya gabata ba.
An kuma ga Red Glow a gundumar Pasco.
An samu matsakaitan taro a gabar tekun Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, low zuwa high a gabar tekun Hillsborough County, low zuwa high a Manatee County, low zuwa high a gabar tekun Sarasota County, low zuwa high a Charlotte County, low zuwa high a gabar tekun Lee County, da low a cikin Collier County.
An samu rahotanni na ci gaba da nuna rashin jin daɗi a cikin hanyoyin numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma Collier.
A arewa maso yammacin Florida babu wani rahoton da ya nuna cewa akwai wani ciwo da ke damun numfashi a makon da ya gabata.
